Ni never got to go to no farm jail neither I got sent to all the worst of the worst maxos like the bay, Bathurst, wello, lithgow, Silverwater and a few others excluding Goulburn!
Im not hating on any of the boys I just really hope these lads mature in there and learn there's more to life then wanting to be the baddest! You 1 4 boys got so much potential don't waste it trying to live up to an image of what you think is cool coz trust me jail ain't a fun place and every single day you're in there you will dream about the day you get your freedom back!
Wish all you young guns the best and stay safe and learn from our mistakes!
Respect from 2759/2148 👊🏼
